---
title: "US60 — Manage feedback + platform activity"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>MonitorScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>TriageFeedback / ResolveContactMessage
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Feedback · ContactMessage
  A->>B: open feedback inbox
  B->>C: markReviewed(feedbackId)
  C->>E: Feedback status → reviewed
  A->>B: open contact request
  B->>C: respond(messageId, reply)
  C->>E: ContactMessage response + resolved
  E-->>C: updated
  B-->>A: queues cleared
  note over E: persisted via SupabaseGateway
